---
---
<section id="certificacion" class="section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cert-grid">
      <div class="cert-text">
        <div class="gold-label">¿POR QUÉ SANTILLÁN?</div>
        <h2 class="cert-heading">Barbero profesional con certificación.</h2>
        <p class="cert-body">Santillán no es solo alguien que corta el pelo — es un profesional formado, certificado, y comprometido con la calidad en cada trabajo.</p>
        <p class="cert-body">Su formación incluye técnicas de colorimetría, corte con tijera y máquina, y tratamientos capilares. Cada servicio está respaldado por conocimiento real.</p>
        <ul class="cert-bullets">
          <li>Formación certificada en barbería</li><li>Experiencia en colorimetría</li><li>Técnica de tijera y máquina</li><li>Garantía de resultado</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="cert-signature"><div class="cert-signature-line"></div><span class="cert-signature-text">— Santillán</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cert-visual">
        <div class="cert-frame" id="certFrame">
          <div class="cert-frame-ornament"></div>
          <div class="cert-frame-small">CERTIFICADO DE</div>
          <div class="cert-frame-title">Barbería Profesional</div>
          <div class="cert-frame-divider"></div>
          <div class="cert-frame-name">Santillán</div>
          <div class="cert-frame-location">Moreno, Buenos Aires</div>
          <div class="cert-frame-ornament-bot"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<style>
  #certificacion { background: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .cert-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 40px; }
  .cert-text { order: 1; }
  .cert-visual { order: 2; }
  .cert-heading {
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 5vw, 52px);
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }
  .cert-body {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.85;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }
  .cert-bullets { margin: 24px 0; }
  .cert-bullets li {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .cert-bullets li::before { content: "✓"; color: var(--gold); margin-right: 6px; }
  .cert-signature { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; margin-top: 28px; }
  .cert-signature-line { width: 80px; height: 1px; background: rgba(201,168,76,0.5); }
  .cert-signature-text {
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 22px;
    color: rgba(201,168,76,0.7);
  }
  .cert-visual { perspective: 1200px; }
  .cert-frame {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 48px 32px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: transform 0.15s cubic-bezier(0.23,1,0.32,1), box-shadow 0.4s ease;
    transform-style: preserve-3d;
    will-change: transform;
  }
  .cert-frame::before,
  .cert-frame::after { transition: border-color 0.4s ease; }
  .cert-frame.tilting { overflow: visible; }
  .cert-frame.tilting::before,
  .cert-frame.tilting::after { pointer-events: none; }
  .cert-frame::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cert-frame::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 10px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .cert-frame-ornament { width: 60px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); margin: 0 auto 16px; }
  .cert-frame-small {
    font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .cert-frame-title {
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 36px);
    color: var(--cream);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .cert-frame-divider { width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); margin: 12px auto; }
  .cert-frame-name {
    font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", Georgia, serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 28px;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  .cert-frame-location { font-family: "DM Sans", sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); }
  .cert-frame-ornament-bot { width: 60px; height: 1px; background: var(--gold); margin: 16px auto 0; }
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .cert-grid { flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 60px; }
    .cert-text { flex: 1; order: 0; }
    .cert-visual { flex: 1; order: 0; }
  }
</style>
